===Etymology===
{{inh|en|enm|auctorite}}, {{m|enm|autorite||authority, book or quotation that settles an argument}}, from {{der|en|fro|auctorité}}, from {{der|en|la|-}} stem of {{m|la|auctōritās||invention, advice, opinion, influence, command}}, from {{m|la|auctor||master, leader, author}}. For the presence of the ''h'', compare the etymology of {{m|en|author}}.

